{"article_id":"ngdg30hkDjx9X1EO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Sunday defended signing the $ 1.3 trillion spending bill","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"and said","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"the amount of money","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"allotted for his border wall","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" is just a down payment . \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Conservatives had criticized the the size of the bill","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"and questioned the lack of funds","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"devoted towards building the president ' s border wall , a top campaign promise .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"\" Because of the $ 700 & $ 716 Billion Dollars","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"gotten","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to rebuild our Military ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"many jobs are created","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and our Military is again rich .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Building a great Border Wall , with drugs","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"( poison )","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and enemy combatants","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"pouring into our Country ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"is all about National Defense .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Build WALL through M ! \"","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Trump tweeted on Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"\" Much can be done with the $ 1.6 Billion","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"given to building and fixing the border wall .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"It is just a down payment .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Work will start immediately .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The rest of the money will come","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"- and remember DACA ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the Democrats abandoned you","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"( but we will not ) ! \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he added .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"The president had first expressed disappointment with Congress on Friday for the more than 2,000-page bill","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"he said","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"no lawmaker read .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"However , he decided not to veto it","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"because of the increase in funds for the U.S. military .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi , California Democrat , touted the $ 1.3 trillion omnibus bill as a win for her party .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"\" Democrats won explicit language","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"restricting border construction to the same see-through fencing","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"that was already authorized under current law , \"","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"she said in a statement last week .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Conservative commentator Ann Coulter agreed","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that the bill was a loss to the president .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"\" I can ' t see anyway","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"to sugar coat what a disaster this is , \"","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"she said on Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Ms. Coulter had been a staunch supporter of the president ' s immigration policies during his campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"but has since voiced frustration over the president ' s delay","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"in building a wall along the southern border .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"\" There was only guy","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that at every speech , at every rally for two years ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that the would build the wall","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and he now signed a bill","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to prohibit the building a wall , \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Ms. Coulter said Saturday on Fox News .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":109,"left":83,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":59,"right":82,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":59,"left":0,"right":58,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":58,"left":1,"right":57,"relation":"attribution",